                  </hi>. I am servant to Mr. John Phillips. On the 7th of July I had a pair of plated waiters, six forks, a pair of ladles, and other things, of my master's—they were quite safe at eleven o'clock in the morning—I missed them about three in the afternoon—these now produced are them—my master's name is on them.</p>
